<h2><a name="_Toc515267290">Beep / Constraints</a></h2>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in'><span style='font-family:
Symbol'>·</span><span style='font-size:7.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>No two consecutive vowels in a syllable.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in'><span style='font-family:
Symbol'>·</span><span style='font-size:7.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>No Bantoc is allowed after a vowel, a pseudo vowel<a name="_ftnref4"></a><a
href="#_ftn4"><span class=MsoFootnoteReference><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:105%'>[4]</span></span></a>, a consonant shifter or a subscript.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in'><span style='font-family:
Symbol'>·</span><span style='font-size:7.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>No two consecutive subscript signs (<span lang=KHM style='font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Khmer Mondulkiri"'>&#6098;</span>) are
allowed.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in'><span style='font-family:
Symbol'>·</span><span style='font-size:7.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>No two consecutive consonant shifters are allowed.</p>

